  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9\u0dcf \u0d9a\u0dd0\u0db4\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0dc4\u0dcf \u0dc3\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0dc3\u0dd3\u0db8\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0dd8\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd3\u0dba \u0db4\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dab \u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0db8\u0dc0\u0dda\u0daf\u0dba",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Professional testing methodology for hair cutting and styling",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "In collaboration with the National Apprenticeship and Industrial Training Authority (NAITA), Dreamron School has made arrangements to offer the 'Hair Cutting Gents - Fashionable Hairdresser' certificate to the current tradesmen through the National Trade Test/NTT.",
        "A national level professional certificate is said to help the youth community to conquer the local and foreign job market. The specialty of this National Professional Test System (NTT) is the availability of knowledge and skill, and the ability of even artisans with short-term experience in the field to apply for the final test. It is said that youth and adults can participate in this test without any age limit.",
        "Representing the National Apprenticeship and Industrial Training Authority, President Tharanga Naleen Gamlath, Vice President Prof. Mahinda Rupasinghe, Director General Dr. W.M.S. Mr. Wijesinghe, Director (Quality) Channa Subasinghe and Assistant Director (Assessment-NVQ) Mr. Sujeeva Wickramasinghe and Dr. Kishu Gomes, Managing Director representing Drimron, Group Director Neesha Perera, Director Sachitra Kalubowila, General Manager Trade (EVON) Nadira Indika Pathyerana, Sr. Dr. Ariya Madurasinghe participated."
      ],
